Commercial Article Writing for ChatGPT
=============================

Write an introduction paragraph with the main keyword: 10 Best Electric Bike With Removable Battery Reviews - 1st person tone
---
Write a product description in a first-person tone, including 4-6 paragraphs with pros and cons bullet points based on the above mentioned details. Each paragraph should begin with a transitional word. The description should be approximately 400 words in length.
